      <ecm_name><![CDATA[Passive Roof Flat External Insulation inverted - XPS 200mm]]></ecm_name>
      <description><![CDATA[An inverted roof construction places thermal insulation above the waterproof layer. This maintains the waterproof membrane at an even temperature and protects it from the damaging effects of UV radiation or the effects of the weather. The specified thermal performance of the inverted roof is achieved through the roof design and the thickness of the insulation used.]]></description>
