      <application><![CDATA[- Where there is a flat roof
- Where there is access to the roof
- Where there is hot climate and applications with neoprene does not work.
- Where there is also external insulation in the facade (optional)
- Where the roof is renovated for making it habitable (optional)]]></application>
      <functional_unit><![CDATA[1 square meter ]]></functional_unit>
      <advantages><![CDATA[- Energy saving: Low heat losses in cold periods and low heat gains in hot months.
- Healthier environment, Comfort: No thermal bridges, and avoid the humidity.
- Aesthetic roof performance
- If you install plots or ceramic (costly) the roof can be practicable]]></advantages>
      <disadvantages><![CDATA[- Sun: In hot weather this solutions is not so used any more due to the degradation of the bituminous layer .
- Snow weight
- No practicable]]></disadvantages>
