      <installation_data><![CDATA[For the installation the major issue to take in to account is the correct installation of the bituminous layer to avoid infiltrations of water into the building. Also the colocation of the insulation layer should be verified in order to avoid possible thermal bridges. And finally the correct protection of the insulation layer with the protection layer (in this case ballast)]]></installation_data>
      <maintenance_data><![CDATA[Revisions should be done in order to check no accumulation of water in any drainage of the roof]]></maintenance_data>
